WEBVTT

00:00:00.670 --> 00:00:05.034
UNK BIRSHUT UNK UNK UNK, UNK mit ayer erloybenish

00:00:05.108 --> 00:00:09.591
geyen mir vayter mit undzer intervyu, mir haltn yetst bay kasete numer zeks,

00:00:09.867 --> 00:00:14.451
un loyt dem vi ikh gedenk, hot ir dertseylt vi ir hot zikh ayngeordent als UNK UNK UNK

00:00:13.663 --> 00:00:17.297
yo, yo, hitst vil ikh aykh zogn vos kh'hob a bisl aroysgelozt.

00:00:17.297 --> 00:00:19.094
azoy vi ikh hob aykh dertseylt frier,

00:00:19.094 --> 00:00:20.694
az kh'hob gehat zeyer a sheynem

00:00:20.818 --> 00:00:22.241
⟨CHAVA⟩ dort in dem

00:00:22.241 --> 00:00:25.743
barg fun SATU MARE, dos iz geven

00:00:24.610 --> 00:00:25.911
far di milkhome

00:00:25.743 --> 00:00:27.101
zeyer sheyn

00:00:27.101 --> 00:00:28.881
un a sakh gute zakhenes,

00:00:28.881 --> 00:00:31.674
iz, in di milkhome iz dokh gevezn milkhome,

00:00:31.674 --> 00:00:33.227
ven ikh bin aheymgekumen

00:00:33.227 --> 00:00:40.556
fun di arbets-dinst oyf CHOFESH, vos iz geven farn geto, in a sheynem tog iz arayngekumen tsu mir a hoykher mentsh, a KATZIN,

00:00:40.680 --> 00:00:45.635
a, bay di, bay di ungarishe armey, vayl s'iz dokh geven daytshn in Ungarn,

00:00:45.675 --> 00:00:47.924
un fregt mikh, zogt er, "du heyst,

00:00:47.958 --> 00:00:50.211
Meyer Mano Daskal?" zog ikh, "yo."

00:00:50.211 --> 00:00:52.976
zogt er, "du veyst," zogt er, "du host bay mayn advokat

00:00:53.016 --> 00:00:55.648
fun mir opgekoyft dem UNK dortn?"

00:00:55.684 --> 00:00:56.603
zog ikh, "yo."

00:00:56.603 --> 00:01:00.171
zogt er, zogt er mir azoy, "her oys," zogt er, "ikh vel dir zogn," zogt er, "a por verter

00:01:00.171 --> 00:01:01.468
in kurtsn," zogt er.

00:01:01.475 --> 00:01:03.846
"un az du vest es veln gut farshteyn," zogt er,

00:01:03.846 --> 00:01:05.279
"vestu es nemen far kentenish."

00:01:05.279 --> 00:01:07.252
"ven nisht," zogt er, "vet dir oyskumen nisht gut."

00:01:07.252 --> 00:01:10.243
zogt er, "her oys, du veyst," zogt er, "azoy vi undz ze'mir hitst in

00:01:10.243 --> 00:01:11.482
in Ungarn,

00:01:11.482 --> 00:01:13.431
un," zogt er, "di daytshn zenen do,"

00:01:13.431 --> 00:01:20.300
"un ikh," zogt er, "vil tsurik hobn mayn git," zogt er, "du vest mir untershraybn az du gibst mir fun dayn gutn viln tsurik," zogt er,

00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:27.623
"un nisht," zogt er, "ikh vel zayn a KATZIN, bay di MUNKASZASZA," zogt er, "du fun dort vest keyn lebediker nisht aheymkumen oyb du vest es nisht tun."

00:01:27.623 --> 00:01:29.944
deys iz geven beforn, farn geto nokh.

00:01:29.944 --> 00:01:32.854
deys hob ikh dertseylt. hitst vel ikh dertseyln vi azoy s'iz geven in Khayfe.

00:01:32.854 --> 00:01:34.820
fun Khayfe vos iz geven di mayse?

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.931
far dem, ikh vel bald tsugebn tsu dem,

00:01:38.059 --> 00:01:41.581
iz azoy vi dey, der iz geven fun di armey mayn

00:01:41.581 --> 00:01:43.871
korev, vos er voynt do,

00:01:43.911 --> 00:01:48.548
un, ikh bin geven der menahel fun dey fuftsik, ober in yene tsayt

00:01:48.548 --> 00:01:50.303
dos heyst in akht in fertsik,

00:01:50.303 --> 00:01:51.527
in nayn un fertsik,

00:01:51.527 --> 00:01:55.686
iz geven shver mit arbet, azoy fil tsu kumen, azoy fun UNK iz geven shver mit arbet,

00:01:55.686 --> 00:02:02.990
flegn araynkumen baym toyer hunderter mentshn vos zey hobn gevolt arbetn, un ikh hob gedarft geyn dort oyskloybn dem yo gebn un yenem nisht gebn,

00:02:03.267 --> 00:02:07.240
deys iz mir geven zeyer nisht gut, vayl vi azoy ken men dem yo gebn, yenem nisht gebn?

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:08.479
ikh veys dokh nisht ver.

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:10.080
un akhuts dem iz mir geven

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:11.039
nokh a zakh,

00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:12.760
az der, der korev mayner,

00:02:12.760 --> 00:02:15.800
kh'hob nisht gekent im nemen, zogn ikh vil im yo arayn un an andern nisht.

00:02:15.911 --> 00:02:17.301
vayl vos vet men zogn?

00:02:17.458 --> 00:02:21.117
iz, hot men alts geklert vos ikh zol tun. dos iz geven eyn sibe.

00:02:21.117 --> 00:02:24.080
der tsveyter sibe iz geven far vos ikh bin gekumen oyf MOSHAV,

00:02:24.120 --> 00:02:24.760
iz geven

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:27.960
vayl kh'hob gehat dortn aza sheynem gortn, mit frukht, mit zakhn,

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:29.280
m'hot geredt fun a MOSHAV,

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.800
hob ikh geklert dos vet oykh zayn azoy vi dort iz gevezn.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:33.920
kh'vel hobn der goy, der goy vet arbetn,

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:35.240
un er vet ales makhn,

00:02:35.240 --> 00:02:36.880
dos vaser vet zikh dreyen, un s'vet zayn...

00:02:36.929 --> 00:02:42.360
 leyder, s'iz geven a groyse toes, vegn dem bin ikh gekumen oyfn MOSHAV. ober,

00:02:42.484 --> 00:02:43.982
kh'hob gearbet in Khayfe,

00:02:43.982 --> 00:02:45.476
un s'iz mir gut gevezn,

00:02:45.476 --> 00:02:48.134
un dos kind iz geboyrn in nayn un fertsik,

00:02:48.134 --> 00:02:50.108
un s'iz gevaksn,

00:02:50.150 --> 00:02:52.648
s'iz alts geven beseyder.

00:02:52.648 --> 00:02:54.982
biz vi lang, in a sheynem tog,

00:02:55.174 --> 00:02:58.897
hob ikh mikh bakent mit eynem vos er iz geven a tseyn dokter, er lebt shoyn nisht.

00:02:59.308 --> 00:03:01.077
vos er hot gevoynt in Khayfe,

00:03:01.077 --> 00:03:06.171
un er hot gehat do UNK ⟨shvogers⟩, in BENAYA, un er hot gezogt,

00:03:06.936 --> 00:03:10.097
kh'hob mit im tsu redt, ikh gedenk shoyn nisht vu, bay KUPAT CHOLIM tsi vu,

00:03:10.097 --> 00:03:12.144
er hot gezogt er hot zeyer gevolt

00:03:12.741 --> 00:03:17.325
m, un me hot im oykh do gegebn a MESHEK, nor er hot nisht gevolt do zayn vayl er iz a tseyn dokter.

00:03:17.668 --> 00:03:20.112
hot er gezogt er volt zeyer gevolt makhn a toysh.

00:03:20.112 --> 00:03:22.522
er hot gevolt ibergebn zayn MESHEK

00:03:22.782 --> 00:03:25.166
un ikh zol ibergebn mayn voynung in Khayfe.

00:03:25.166 --> 00:03:27.781
ikh hot gevoynt dort nisht vayt funem

00:03:27.781 --> 00:03:31.432
fun groysn KUPAT CHOLIM, dort iz do dey

00:03:31.472 --> 00:03:34.211
dey nones fun Frankraykh hobn dort voynungen.

00:03:34.211 --> 00:03:36.039
dort in dey voynungen ho'mir gevoynt.

00:03:36.197 --> 00:03:38.565
un ho'mir gemakht mit yenem a gesheft,

00:03:38.565 --> 00:03:41.687
un azoy ze'mir undz ongekumen oyf BENAYA.

00:03:41.243 --> 00:03:42.131
ven zent ir ongekumen?

00:03:42.243 --> 00:03:44.595
in BENAYA ze'mir ongekumen aher

00:03:44.702 --> 00:03:46.839
in in

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:49.589
in fuftsiker yor

00:03:49.967 --> 00:03:52.914
yo, in fuftsiker yor, nokh ROSH-HASHANA.

00:03:53.427 --> 00:03:54.821
ze'mir ongekumen aher

00:03:54.625 --> 00:03:58.534
yetst zayt azoy gut, dertseylt mir in kurtsn vi ir ordnt zikh ayn do in BENAYA.

00:03:58.033 --> 00:03:58.772
yo.

00:03:58.772 --> 00:04:00.030
hitster iz azoy.

00:04:00.030 --> 00:04:05.486
az ze'mir gekumen aher, hob ikh gemakht, mit dem mitn korev, hob ikh gemakht azoy,

00:04:05.695 --> 00:04:08.040
heyder m'iz aroysgeforn fun Khayfe,

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:10.800
hob ikh gezogt azoy, vayl kh'hob shoyn gehert UNK me hot gefregt,

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:12.240
vos heyst a MOSHAV,

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:14.840
hot men gezogt a MOSHAV iz zeyer shtark farkoyft,

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:16.360
m'hot keyn mol nisht keyn

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:18.044
 keyn CHOFESH,

00:04:18.044 --> 00:04:22.491
az me darf shtendik zayn, vayl az m'hot kuen darf men melkn, darf men deys, darf men yents,

00:04:22.491 --> 00:04:25.469
hob ikh geklert azoy, az mit im, kh'vel makhn a shutfes,

00:04:25.469 --> 00:04:28.658
ho'mir opgeredt, kuk, vel'mir zayn tsvey ire, nokh dem du vest khasene hobn

00:04:28.658 --> 00:04:32.720
az ikh vel veln avekgeyn CHOFESH oyf akht tog, vestu blaybn, vestu firn di virtshaft,

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:34.320
un az du vest veln vestu geyn.

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:36.920
ikh hob azoy gemeynt, ober ikh hob gehat a groysn toes, nu,

00:04:36.944 --> 00:04:37.956
oykh farfaln.

00:04:37.956 --> 00:04:40.687
iz durkh dem ze'mir undz gekumen oyfn MOSHAV aroyf.

00:04:40.727 --> 00:04:44.214
m'iz gekumen oyfn MOSHAV, er iz do geven, er hot gearbet a shtikl tsayt,

00:04:44.406 --> 00:04:47.153
der UNK hot gehat a mashin vos hot gefirt di milekh

00:04:47.153 --> 00:04:48.905
demolt iz nokh nisht geven azoy vi hitstert,

00:04:49.232 --> 00:04:50.154
ober,

00:04:51.072 --> 00:04:52.832
er hot nisht gevolt zayn do.

00:04:52.832 --> 00:04:55.537
nokh dem hot zikh im getrofn, s'iz gekumen a meydl fun Ungarn,

00:04:55.611 --> 00:04:58.068
un me hot gemakht a khasene, er hot khasene gehat.

00:04:58.227 --> 00:04:59.638
ober zi,

00:05:02.648 --> 00:05:05.817
fun Budapest, iz shoyn geven mer a bisele kluger vi er,

00:05:05.817 --> 00:05:07.806
un zi hot gezen az me hot in shtal

00:05:08.014 --> 00:05:10.069
etlekhe kep fun beheymes,

00:05:10.069 --> 00:05:12.854
un er iz do, az deys iz halb zayer.

00:05:12.854 --> 00:05:17.655
ober nisht dos iz geven der feler, der feler iz gevezn, az er iz avekgeforn mit di milekh fun do

00:05:17.655 --> 00:05:19.612
vos er hot gehat oyf a sho arbet

00:05:19.612 --> 00:05:25.794
un iz tsurikgekumen in fir sho arum, vayl er hot nisht gevolt arbetn UNK, un zi oyf azoy fil nisht vayl zi iz geven a Budapester,

00:05:26.037 --> 00:05:28.478
hot zikh gemakht dos gesheft oyf.

00:05:28.990 --> 00:05:33.467
un zi hot gezogt nor azoy az zi bakumt fun di beheymes vi fil s'iz do, di helft.

00:05:33.467 --> 00:05:36.690
hob ikh gezogt koydem hob ikh gekoyft ale beheymes, dos iz numer eyns.

00:05:36.690 --> 00:05:37.584
khuts im.

00:05:37.584 --> 00:05:38.781
un tsveytn teyl,

00:05:38.781 --> 00:05:39.943
se ken nisht zayn andersh,

00:05:39.943 --> 00:05:41.297
shoyn, me hot gehaltn

00:05:41.297 --> 00:05:43.201
UNK UNK UNK UNK UNK

00:05:43.201 --> 00:05:46.007
biz vi lang ze'mir gekumen oyf a, oyf a oysveg.

00:05:46.007 --> 00:05:47.781
ikh hob ⟨im⟩ gekoyft a MESHEK do

00:05:47.781 --> 00:05:50.223
demolt in yene tsayt, me hot ibergelozt dem UNK

00:05:50.223 --> 00:05:51.832
far dray toyznt shekl.

00:05:52.530 --> 00:05:54.059
deys iz geven in in,

00:05:54.235 --> 00:05:56.459
ikh veys ven, etlekhe fuftsiker yor.

00:05:56.459 --> 00:05:57.783
kh'hob im gekoyft a MESHEK.

00:05:57.783 --> 00:06:01.336
un er voynt do, UNK, un er lebt, er hot haynt tsvey dray mashinen.

00:06:01.336 --> 00:06:02.498
er hot tsvey zin.

00:06:02.605 --> 00:06:06.564
un undz ho'mir ongehoybn tsu arbetn do. di arbet iz geven zeyer shver.

00:06:06.874 --> 00:06:08.117
shtark shver.

00:06:08.187 --> 00:06:09.925
nor vi azoy den?

00:06:09.925 --> 00:06:15.915
me ho'mir gekent makhn, shoyn shpeter ven m'iz tsu zikh gekumen, ho'mir gekent makhn a por pyaster. vi azoy?

00:06:15.915 --> 00:06:19.810
me vet ven nisht gekent makhn funem tog teglekhn lebn het men ven nisht gekent makhn.

00:06:19.822 --> 00:06:24.840
vayl s'iz, di parnose iz geven azoy kleyn, az s'iz nisht geven fun vos optsushporn.

00:06:25.032 --> 00:06:28.868
nokh dem iz gevorn an andere mayse, m'hot ongehoybn tsu koyfn di ⟨BIKES⟩

00:06:28.868 --> 00:06:30.917
lemoshl az a ku hot gehat a UNK

00:06:30.917 --> 00:06:33.947
me hot es oyfgevaksn, se hot gevoygn finef zeks hundert kilo,

00:06:33.947 --> 00:06:35.719
hot men bakumen sheyn gelt.

00:06:35.719 --> 00:06:38.322
ober deys hot men gedarft UNK, vos ho'mir undz getun?

00:06:38.494 --> 00:06:41.074
undz ze'mir gezesn bay tog un bay nakht oyfn feld,

00:06:41.074 --> 00:06:42.881
un me hot gekoshet, un me hot gebrengt

00:06:42.913 --> 00:06:44.784
me zol nisht darfn koyfn dey UNK,

00:06:44.913 --> 00:06:47.558
un me hot farkoyft aza ⟨bik⟩, un me hot opgeshport dos gelt,

00:06:47.558 --> 00:06:48.848
me hot es geleygt in tash.

00:06:48.848 --> 00:06:52.203
azoy is geven a tsvey dray yor biz me hot tsamgeshtelt a bisele gelt.

00:06:52.203 --> 00:06:55.656
azoy vi arum, az fun do ven di tokhter is aroysgegangen

00:06:55.656 --> 00:06:57.492
un zi hot zikh bakent mit a bokher,

00:06:58.292 --> 00:07:01.774
d- der tsveyter, zi hot zikh bakent mit a bokher vos zi hot khasene gehat,

00:07:01.867 --> 00:07:04.900
ho'mir ir gekoyft a voynung in RAMATAIM,

00:07:04.900 --> 00:07:06.351
un,

00:07:06.351 --> 00:07:07.835
undz ze'mir geblibn do,

00:07:07.835 --> 00:07:09.061
un BARUCH hashem,

00:07:09.061 --> 00:07:13.416
nor vos, vos ikh bin nisht gezunt, di fis tuen mikh vey vos ikh ken nisht geyn,

00:07:13.416 --> 00:07:17.341
kh'hob bakumen tsveyerley krankeytn, vos iz epes a min UNK, un nokh a zakh,

00:07:17.341 --> 00:07:20.234
az leyder, leyder, dray, fir shpan ken ikh nisht geyn.

00:07:20.234 --> 00:07:22.137
az ikh gey shabes in shil,

00:07:22.137 --> 00:07:28.266
iz mit shvere mi, darf ikh unter vegns shteyn blaybn mi- mikh aropzetsn opruen, vayl ikh gey mit a shtekn,

00:07:28.266 --> 00:07:31.846
azoy in der fri, ikh shtey oyf bin ikh nokh a mentsh, as me kukt mikh on dakht zikh

00:07:31.846 --> 00:07:33.266
az ikh bin nokh epes a mentsh.

00:07:33.266 --> 00:07:34.871
ober azoy leyder iz,

00:07:35.316 --> 00:07:38.550
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt fregn, di tokhter, vos hot zi gelernt?

00:07:36.615 --> 00:07:37.503
yo.

00:07:38.033 --> 00:07:41.188
di tokhter hot gelernt in a shule, zi iz a MORAH

00:07:41.188 --> 00:07:42.671
far hoykhe klasn,

00:07:42.671 --> 00:07:45.671
un akhuts dem hot zi gelernt in BAR-ILAN

00:07:45.671 --> 00:07:46.954
alts,

00:07:46.993 --> 00:07:51.318
kriminolog, zi hot a TEUDA, TEUDA hengt do oyf di vant.

00:07:51.318 --> 00:07:55.188
alts kriminolog, ober zi lernt alts in di hoykhe shul, in RAMATAIM.

00:07:55.188 --> 00:08:02.155
un der eydem iz, dokter, in, UNK in UNK.

00:08:02.417 --> 00:08:05.282
yetst, fun di tokhter hot ir vifl eyniklekh?

00:08:05.202 --> 00:08:07.508
fun di tokhter tsvey eyniklekh.

00:08:05.282 --> 00:08:06.427
zoln zayn gezunt.

00:08:07.581 --> 00:08:11.253
a zun, un a tokhter, un dos driter iz der eydem far di tokhter.

00:08:11.783 --> 00:08:13.954
oykh a UNK, un UNK

00:08:12.643 --> 00:08:16.935
yetst, vos makhn di eyniklekh, bay vos, mit vos basheftikn zikh di eyniklekh?

00:08:15.630 --> 00:08:18.789
di eyniklekh basheftikn, zey zenen in di armey.

00:08:18.789 --> 00:08:20.273
zey hobn untergeshribn

00:08:20.273 --> 00:08:22.725
un zey muzn oysdinen. nisht vayl zey hobn

00:08:22.725 --> 00:08:24.466
kholile far gelt, zey hobn far eygenem

00:08:24.466 --> 00:08:26.499
nor zey hobn untergeshribn zey veln zayn dortn.

00:08:26.499 --> 00:08:27.558
dos heyst, s'iz do

00:08:27.558 --> 00:08:33.765
dem, dem, m- meydl's di di tokhter's, der eydem,

00:08:34.496 --> 00:08:38.387
un der eynikl. der eynikl darf dem zumer bafrayt vern,

00:08:38.450 --> 00:08:41.933
der eynikl iz der KATZIN, vos er hot geratevet

00:08:41.933 --> 00:08:45.258
dey UNK fun england

00:08:45.321 --> 00:08:50.256
vayl me hot geharget dem man, in NEGEV. kh'hob nokh do dort a bild fun ir oyfn tsay-

00:08:50.256 --> 00:08:51.934
fun im, fun do, in tsaytung.

00:08:51.934 --> 00:08:54.347
un zey zenen hitst in di armey ale dray.

00:08:54.347 --> 00:08:58.132
dos heyst dos eynikl, der man, un dos andere eynikl.

00:08:57.784 --> 00:09:00.709
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage.

00:08:59.455 --> 00:09:00.208
yo.

00:09:01.227 --> 00:09:03.448
loyt dem vos ir hot dertseylt

00:09:05.513 --> 00:09:07.836
iz ayer yetstike froy

00:09:08.010 --> 00:09:10.636
a ibergelebte, un ir zent a ibergelebte.

00:09:08.820 --> 00:09:11.008
ibergelebt, iber- yo.

00:09:12.567 --> 00:09:13.686
tsi hot ir

00:09:13.686 --> 00:09:17.677
di ale yorn, ven ir, ven d-, ven ayer tokhter is oyfgevaksn,

00:09:17.686 --> 00:09:22.774
hot zi zikh gefregt, far mir, dertseylt di kinde- di tokhter, di eyniklekh, vos me hot als adurkhgemakht?

00:09:20.852 --> 00:09:21.622
yo.

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:26.634
nu, koydem, dos ershte mol nisht, ho'mir nisht gevolt dertseyln.

00:09:26.758 --> 00:09:29.067
vayl me hot geklert, s'iz genug in undz

00:09:29.067 --> 00:09:32.029
kh'hob mikh aleyn nisht gevolt dermanen, vayl ikh zog nokh, afile haynt,

00:09:32.029 --> 00:09:36.129
kler ikh a sakh mol az s'iz gornisht emes, s'iz nisht meglekh az ikh zol zayn do.

00:09:36.129 --> 00:09:37.419
ho'mir nisht gevolt dertseyln,

00:09:37.452 --> 00:09:40.000
ober nokh dem hobn di eyniklekh ongehoybn fregn,

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:41.613
nisht di tokhter, nor di eyniklekh,

00:09:41.613 --> 00:09:43.968
azoy arum az me ho'mir dertseylt

00:09:43.968 --> 00:09:46.220
far di tokhter un far di eyniklekh, zey veysn

00:09:46.220 --> 00:09:47.613
aldings, genoy,

00:09:47.613 --> 00:09:49.736
vos s'iz geshen un vi azoy s'iz geshen.

00:09:49.422 --> 00:09:52.217
nokh a kurtse frage, mit ayer erloybenish.

00:09:50.805 --> 00:09:51.659
yo.

00:09:52.645 --> 00:09:55.727
b-, loyt dem vos, di ale tsores vos ir hot adurkhgemakht,

00:09:53.944 --> 00:09:57.498
yo, yo, ikh, ikh vil aykh epes dertseyln nokh a zakh.

00:09:56.170 --> 00:09:57.870
bite. bite.

00:09:57.673 --> 00:09:58.733
iz,

00:09:58.733 --> 00:10:01.193
ikh vil aykh dertseyln, in shaykhes mit dem,

00:10:01.193 --> 00:10:05.138
ershtn CHALOM mayne, mitn kholem, vil ikh aykh dertseyln,

00:10:05.138 --> 00:10:07.888
az nokh dem vi ikh hob getrofn di tsveyte

00:10:07.888 --> 00:10:10.458
in Satu-Mare ven ikh bin geforn zi zukhn,

00:10:10.650 --> 00:10:12.225
hot zi mir dertseylt

00:10:12.225 --> 00:10:16.011
"du veyst," zogt zi, "dem ershtn oyf der nakht, fraytog oyf der nakht,"

00:10:16.050 --> 00:10:22.726
"in Oyshvits, oyf dey pritshn ven me hot zikh nisht gekent rurn, hob ikh gekholemt a tayern kholem."

00:10:22.733 --> 00:10:29.429
"in der kholem," zogt zi, "hot mikh gehaltn biz ende. ikh hob gekholemt ikh zits bay mayn tatn baym tish,"

00:10:29.429 --> 00:10:33.023
"un der tate shnaydt fun di groyse khale far yedn,"

00:10:33.023 --> 00:10:41.267
"un s'iz ales azoy sheyn un voyl," zogt zi, "un kh'hob dervekt in Oyshvits oyfn pritshn." deys hob ikh gevolt dertseyln fun ir. un, nokh a kholem hot zi dertseylt.

00:10:41.267 --> 00:10:43.714
zi iz bafrayt gevorn in THERESIENSTADT.

00:10:43.714 --> 00:10:46.993
deys iz geven im nayntn ⟨marts⟩, shpeter vu ikh.

00:10:47.050 --> 00:10:49.401
un zi iz arayngefaln in a tifus.

00:10:49.401 --> 00:10:51.330
vi azoy iz zi arayngefaln in a tifus?

00:10:51.387 --> 00:10:54.226
di shvegerins ire zenen bald dem andern tog geganen

00:10:54.226 --> 00:10:56.678
organizirn, dort hot men gezogt organizirn,

00:10:56.774 --> 00:10:58.581
broyt un fleysh, un vu me hot gekent,

00:10:58.581 --> 00:11:00.484
zi hot getrofn ergets in a keler

00:11:00.504 --> 00:11:03.634
kartofl, mit shinke. shinke.

00:11:03.634 --> 00:11:07.411
un zi hot gebrengt, un zi hot opgekokht a groysn top shinke mit kartofl.

00:11:07.671 --> 00:11:09.094
un mayne

00:11:09.094 --> 00:11:13.962
hot oykh gegesn, vayl m'iz dokh hungerik geven dortn, un s'iz ir gekumen arayn in moyl, un se hot ir geglitsht,

00:11:13.962 --> 00:11:16.721
un zi hot zikh zeyer fargroylt, zi hot gezen az dos iz shinke.

00:11:16.721 --> 00:11:19.033
fun dem fargroyl iz zi arayngefaln in tifus.

00:11:19.033 --> 00:11:22.244
un s'iz geven dort akht, tsen tog tifus in bet.

00:11:22.403 --> 00:11:26.829
un befor mit tsvey tog heyder s'iz geven der krizis bayn ir,

00:11:26.829 --> 00:11:33.385
hot zi mir dertseylt, iz arayngekumen a rusisher dokter, un tsvey shvester, un zey hobn gehat in di hent aza ⟨CHOVERET⟩

00:11:33.385 --> 00:11:43.662
un zey hobn ongehoybn oyftsushraybn, vayl s'iz geven di ende fun di tifusnikes dortn, vayl fun deye iz veynik oyfgeshtanen. me hot zi gefregt ver zi iz fun der heym, oyb zi hot nokh emetsn in der velt, az

00:11:43.662 --> 00:11:47.239
m'hot ir nisht gezogt far vos, nor me zol kenen nokh dem tsu visn gebn.

00:11:47.239 --> 00:11:48.164
zogt zi,

00:11:48.778 --> 00:11:51.100
di elefte nakht fun tifus,

00:11:51.141 --> 00:11:53.160
zogt zi, zi iz gelegn in a hits,

00:11:54.887 --> 00:11:57.209
se hot zikh gegosn dos vaser fun ir,

00:11:57.739 --> 00:11:59.488
zi hot nisht gevust fun zikh.

00:11:59.646 --> 00:12:01.496
zogt zi, plutsem kholemt zi

00:12:02.700 --> 00:12:04.671
az der ⟨rabay⟩ kumt un shrayt,

00:12:04.671 --> 00:12:10.963
"du zest nisht, Perl, gey arop funem RAKEVET! funem PASEY RAKEVET! der RAKEVET kumt er vet dikh iberforn."

00:12:11.644 --> 00:12:17.865
zogt zi, "un azoy shrayendik iz er tsugekumen un hot mikh ongekhapt un hot mikh aropgeshlept. demolt hob ikh mikh dervekt."

00:12:18.158 --> 00:12:22.860
"s'iz lebn mir geshtanen ACHOT, a rusishe, un zi hot mir gegebn HAZRAKAH."

00:12:23.187 --> 00:12:25.121
un demolt iz ir beser gevorn.

00:12:25.279 --> 00:12:31.365
deys iz khaloymes, me zogt me gleybt nisht in khaloymes, ober epes iz in dem. deys hob ikh gevolt tsugebn.

00:12:31.067 --> 00:12:33.676
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a kurtse frage.

00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:33.947
yo.

00:12:34.611 --> 00:12:38.807
nokh dem vi ir hot alts dertseylt vos ir hot alts adurkhgemakht, oyb ir kukt

00:12:36.265 --> 00:12:37.119
yo.

00:12:38.931 --> 00:12:41.119
tsurik, vos se hot alts pasirt,

00:12:39.825 --> 00:12:40.764
yo.

00:12:41.310 --> 00:12:43.683
vi hot er gevirkt oyf ayer lebn?

00:12:43.960 --> 00:12:49.517
un zo- nu zog ikh dokh aykh, deys hot gevirkt oyf farshidene zakhn.

00:12:44.193 --> 00:12:46.483
di ale tsores. bizn hayntikn tog.

00:12:49.517 --> 00:12:53.117
koydem hot gevirkt oyf dem, az se kumt a normale mentsh oyf a plats,

00:12:53.224 --> 00:12:56.086
vu er bakumt a tog a bisele shvarts vaser,

00:12:56.177 --> 00:12:57.470
mit efsher

00:12:57.662 --> 00:12:59.900
ikh veys, efsher tsvey hundert gram

00:12:59.991 --> 00:13:02.468
broyt, vos dos iz fun a hart breytl.

00:13:02.468 --> 00:13:05.182
hot gevirkt mayne ale tsen demoltsdike

00:13:05.222 --> 00:13:06.971
zenen aroysgefaln.

00:13:07.230 --> 00:13:09.232
ikh bin krank gevorn oyfn mogn.

00:13:09.525 --> 00:13:11.375
biz im hayntikn tog.

00:13:11.500 --> 00:13:14.433
un, ikh ken aykh zogn dem emes,

00:13:14.433 --> 00:13:16.580
vi azoy ikh hob dos dertseylt far aykh veys ikh nisht,

00:13:16.580 --> 00:13:18.323
vayl ikh zog az ikh bin nisht normal.

00:13:18.323 --> 00:13:21.000
vayl oyb a mentsh ken fun Oyshvits aroyskumen

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:22.936
un hern mit zayne oyern

00:13:22.936 --> 00:13:26.546
az mayn froy, un kinder, un muter geyen in flamen,

00:13:27.025 --> 00:13:28.571
ken nisht zayn klor.

00:13:28.965 --> 00:13:30.438
zog ikh oyf mir.

00:13:30.438 --> 00:13:31.848
ikh veys nisht andere,

00:13:31.848 --> 00:13:34.421
azoy gevirkt es, un se virkt biz haynt,

00:13:34.421 --> 00:13:37.906
vayl ikh hob azoy fil khaloymes gehat, vos ikh shtey oyf in der fri,

00:13:37.906 --> 00:13:40.168
gist zikh dos vaser fun mir, ikh veys nisht far vos,

00:13:40.168 --> 00:13:43.071
vayl ikh bahalt mikh far di S.S., ikh veys nisht vos tsu ton.

00:13:44.288 --> 00:13:47.724
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn, rikhtik, nisht keyn frage,

00:13:47.427 --> 00:13:48.231
yo.

00:13:48.118 --> 00:13:49.968
nor ven ven ikh volt aykh gezogt

00:13:50.430 --> 00:13:56.533
ven ir darft shikn a telegram tsu di tsukumftike doyres, tsu di doyre-doyres, in der tsukumft,

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:53.208
yo.

00:13:54.868 --> 00:13:55.706
yo.

00:13:56.067 --> 00:13:56.888
yo.

00:13:56.792 --> 00:14:01.443
vos far a eytse volt ir zey gegebn alts, nokh dem vos ir hot alts adurkhgemakht?

00:14:00.623 --> 00:14:01.539
yo.

00:14:01.539 --> 00:14:03.682
ikh het gegebn eyn eytse.

00:14:03.682 --> 00:14:06.202
in meynstn teyl farn yidishn folk.

00:14:06.597 --> 00:14:08.835
az vu se gefint zikh eyner,

00:14:09.060 --> 00:14:10.980
un iber hoypt di yugntlekhe,

00:14:10.980 --> 00:14:12.795
hobn zey eyn plats

00:14:12.795 --> 00:14:14.837
dos iz in ERETZ-YISRAEL.

00:14:14.837 --> 00:14:17.695
un ergets in der velt veln zey deys nisht hobn.

00:14:17.751 --> 00:14:21.849
vayl undz ho'mir oykh gehat gute tsaytn, me hot gemeynt az keyn besers iz nisht do.

00:14:21.849 --> 00:14:24.096
ober leyder sof iz geven nisht gut.

00:14:24.139 --> 00:14:27.074
un azoy iz iberal mit di best fraynt vos me hot.

00:14:27.107 --> 00:14:29.816
ven se kumt tsum sof iz nisht do keyn fraynt.

00:14:29.889 --> 00:14:32.595
iz di beste zakh vos ikh vintsh far ale yidn,

00:14:32.871 --> 00:14:35.987
meyle, di kristn veln undz helfn, s'iz do eyntsele vos zenen

00:14:36.043 --> 00:14:39.044
dey vos zey geyen in Yad-Vashem, dos zenen eyntsele,

00:14:39.044 --> 00:14:41.623
ober di yidn hobn nisht keyn ander plats

00:14:41.623 --> 00:14:43.462
afile ven zey shepn gold,

00:14:43.462 --> 00:14:45.849
zoln zey visn az deys iz nor tsaytvaylik.

00:14:45.849 --> 00:14:47.507
ober leoylom-habe,

00:14:47.507 --> 00:14:50.465
iz undzer erd do. do, do.

00:14:52.176 --> 00:14:55.292
s'iz nokh epes vos ir hot gevolt tsugebn tsu ayer SIPUR?

00:14:55.652 --> 00:14:57.285
vos ir hot zikh epes dermant

00:14:57.285 --> 00:14:58.295
spetsyel?

00:14:58.588 --> 00:15:01.366
vayl tomer nisht geyen mir ariber tsu di...

00:15:00.529 --> 00:15:02.986
yo. ikh vel aykh zogn.

00:15:02.993 --> 00:15:04.455
kh'hob mikh dermant

00:15:04.596 --> 00:15:05.748
az,

00:15:05.748 --> 00:15:07.790
loyt vi do in land firt zikh,

00:15:07.790 --> 00:15:10.355
s'iz leyder az undz tsvishn undz,

00:15:10.355 --> 00:15:11.812
ho'mir nisht keyn sholem.

00:15:11.886 --> 00:15:14.701
deys iz der vikhtikster prat, iber alemen.

00:15:14.701 --> 00:15:17.283
ven se het geven az eyn yid mitn andern,

00:15:17.283 --> 00:15:19.637
tsi er iz a CHILONI, tsi er iz a DAATI,

00:15:19.637 --> 00:15:21.012
het geven fareynikt,

00:15:21.012 --> 00:15:22.916
het andersh geven bayn undz in land.

00:15:23.091 --> 00:15:29.987
deys eyne bet ikh got ikh zol nokh kenen khotsh azoy fil lebn, az deys zol zayn fareynikt, vet mayn harts zayn oyfn plats.

00:15:30.027 --> 00:15:31.590
vayl ikh zog aykh,

00:15:31.748 --> 00:15:36.022
az mayn lebn iz far mayn tokhter, un far di tsvey eyniklekh vos ikh ze.

00:15:36.022 --> 00:15:37.355
ikh ze zey,

00:15:37.355 --> 00:15:39.949
deys git mir tsu yedn tog mut.

00:15:39.949 --> 00:15:44.634
deys hob ikh gevolt tsugebn.

00:15:40.843 --> 00:15:44.532
ikh hob aykh gevolt danken far dem vikhtikn teyl vos ir dertseylt.

00:15:44.775 --> 00:15:45.933
TODA RABA

00:15:44.978 --> 00:15:48.279
veln mir ariber geyn yetst oyf dem teyl fun di fotografyes.

00:15:53.567 --> 00:16:01.998
her Meyir, yetst geyen mir ariber tsu dem teyl fun di bilder. zayt azoy gut, zogt mir fun vanet hot ir di bilder fun der heym, di historishe bilder?

00:16:01.718 --> 00:16:05.475
deys historishe bild, dem SABA un di SAVTA,

00:16:05.548 --> 00:16:07.334
hob ikh gehat a mume

00:16:07.334 --> 00:16:20.477
deys heyst mayn mame's a shvester, un zi hot gevoynt do in ERETZ-YISRAEL. un zi hot gehat deys bild fun far di milkhome. azoy bin ikh gekumen, mit ir zun, hot es mir gebrengt, a kleyn bildele, un ikh hob es fargresert.

00:16:19.977 --> 00:16:22.367
verzhe iz oyfn bild, zogt mir di nemen.

00:16:21.478 --> 00:16:28.070
oyf dem bild, di nemen heyst Khane heyst di SAVTA, un Shmuel heyst der SABA, hot geheysn.

00:16:27.840 --> 00:16:29.960
ven hobn zey geshtorbn?

00:16:29.190 --> 00:16:30.972
zey zenen geshtorbn...

00:16:30.253 --> 00:16:31.833
zikhroynem livrokhe?

00:16:31.435 --> 00:16:34.281
 der SABA iz geshtorbn

00:16:34.371 --> 00:16:36.789
in in nayn im draysiker yor.

00:16:36.789 --> 00:16:40.912
un di SAVTA iz geshtorbn in in

00:16:42.319 --> 00:16:44.118
dray un fertsiker yor.

00:16:47.196 --> 00:16:51.881
vi arum hot ir di andere bilder fun far ⟨di krig⟩, un ayer froy's bilder?

00:16:52.022 --> 00:16:53.349
deys bild

00:16:53.355 --> 00:16:54.862
ho'mir undz bakumen

00:16:54.862 --> 00:16:59.090
fun der shvegerin, fun mayn froy's a shvester, i fun der ershter, i fun der tsveyter,

00:16:59.090 --> 00:17:01.123
ho'mir bakumen deys in MEXICO.

00:17:01.123 --> 00:17:05.516
zi hot undz gegebn deys, men hot gemakht a kopye, un me hot gebrengt dos bild aheym.

00:17:05.016 --> 00:17:06.832
un oykh ire bilder.

00:17:06.196 --> 00:17:07.118
oykh ir bilder.

00:17:07.159 --> 00:17:08.705
verzhe iz oyfn bild?

00:17:08.204 --> 00:17:11.033
oyfn bild bin ikh un mayn ershte froy.

00:17:10.534 --> 00:17:12.165
velkhe yor iz dos?

00:17:11.597 --> 00:17:13.464
deys iz draysiker yor.

00:17:13.335 --> 00:17:15.657
vi hot geheysn ayer ershte froy?

00:17:15.022 --> 00:17:16.011
Helen.

00:17:15.900 --> 00:17:17.666
un vos hot mir ir pasirt?

00:17:18.212 --> 00:17:21.615
vos heyst vos hot mit ir pasirt, mit di kinder, in Oyshvits umgekumen!

00:17:22.363 --> 00:17:24.601
vi hobn geheysn ayere kinder, gedenkt ir?

00:17:24.102 --> 00:17:25.277
yo, yo,

00:17:24.777 --> 00:17:26.205
UNK

00:17:25.317 --> 00:17:26.391
Edit.

00:17:26.633 --> 00:17:27.760
Betsalel.

00:17:27.760 --> 00:17:31.756
nokh mayn foter. Nokh dem iz geven Reyzi, Malka.

00:17:35.593 --> 00:17:37.764
ver iz oyf dem bild, bite?

00:17:37.146 --> 00:17:41.325
oyf dem bild iz mayn gevezenem shver olev-hasholem,

00:17:41.162 --> 00:17:42.523
vi hot er geheysn?

00:17:42.208 --> 00:17:44.834
er hot geheysn Sruel-Mekhl.

00:17:45.448 --> 00:17:48.128
un ahintern, un dos andere

00:17:48.128 --> 00:17:50.347
iz di shtif-muter far mayn froy,

00:17:50.347 --> 00:17:52.631
un ahinter iz mayn froy, di tsveyte.

00:17:52.587 --> 00:17:56.040
vos hot pasirt mit di mentshn vos zenen oyfn bild, akhuts ayer froy?

00:17:55.253 --> 00:17:58.824
akhuts mayn froy zenen zey umgekumen in Oyshvits.

00:18:01.800 --> 00:18:02.638
bite.

00:18:03.792 --> 00:18:05.890
deys iz mayne shvoger.

00:18:05.890 --> 00:18:07.872
deys heyst dos iz a bruder

00:18:07.872 --> 00:18:11.880
gevezn far mayn froy, far di ershte un far di tsveyte.

00:18:11.880 --> 00:18:14.096
er hot geheysn Meyer Ber.

00:18:14.777 --> 00:18:16.813
zi hot geheysn Khane.

00:18:17.123 --> 00:18:25.200
deys iz di froy vos zi iz geven UNK. zey zenen umgekumen mit di kinder in Oyshvits. zey hobn gehat...

00:18:22.742 --> 00:18:24.035
vifl kinder hobn zey gehat?

00:18:25.223 --> 00:18:26.704
tsvey

00:18:26.704 --> 00:18:27.933
dray kinder.

00:18:31.770 --> 00:18:36.711
deys bild iz mayn shvester's shvester.

00:18:36.711 --> 00:18:37.893
iz der man.

00:18:37.893 --> 00:18:39.830
zi hot geheysn Ides,

00:18:39.837 --> 00:18:41.468
un er hot geheysn,

00:18:42.013 --> 00:18:44.943
 nu, vi azoy hot er shoyn geheysn?

00:18:45.540 --> 00:18:47.356
s'iz mir yetst aroys funem kop,

00:18:47.937 --> 00:18:49.163
 Yidl.

00:18:49.168 --> 00:18:49.907
Yidl.

00:18:49.894 --> 00:18:51.204
vos iz geshen mit zey?

00:18:49.907 --> 00:18:51.300
hot er geheysn.

00:18:52.043 --> 00:18:56.494
zi iz umgekumen in Oyshvits vayl zi iz mit undz geforn, mit a kleyn kind.

00:18:56.494 --> 00:18:58.806
un er iz umgekumen in MATHAUSEN.

00:18:58.806 --> 00:19:02.677
in Mathoyzn. er hot nisht gevolt aroysgeyn demolt ven ikh bin aroysgegan,

00:19:02.733 --> 00:19:04.316
m'hot gerufn TAFSANIM.

00:19:10.903 --> 00:19:11.487
bite.

00:19:12.388 --> 00:19:13.816
deys bild

00:19:14.228 --> 00:19:16.190
iz mayn froy's a bruder.

00:19:16.190 --> 00:19:18.511
i far di ershte, i far di tsveyte,

00:19:18.511 --> 00:19:21.158
un deys iz zayn froy vos er hot geheyrat mit ir.

00:19:21.467 --> 00:19:22.996
er iz umgekumen

00:19:23.138 --> 00:19:24.617
keyn Oyshvits,

00:19:25.602 --> 00:19:28.617
 neyn in MATHAUSEN, oykh in Mathoyzn,

00:19:28.617 --> 00:19:31.193
zi is geshtorbn do nokh di milkhome,

00:19:31.290 --> 00:19:34.580
do in Erets-Yisroel, iz zi gevezn, iz zi do geshtorbn.

00:19:34.719 --> 00:19:36.077
zi hob gevoynt in,

00:19:36.077 --> 00:19:37.576
in KIRYAT UNK.

00:19:41.363 --> 00:19:42.538
deys bild

00:19:42.780 --> 00:19:44.967
iz a kurtse tsayt nokh di milkhome,

00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:47.032
hob ikh gevolt s'zol blaybn an en- an andenk.

00:19:47.032 --> 00:19:48.741
nokh di geshtrayfte kleyder,

00:19:48.799 --> 00:19:51.483
hob ikh gemakht dort a bild in Munkhen.

00:19:53.563 --> 00:19:54.417
bite.

00:19:54.998 --> 00:20:00.352
deys bild is a kurtse tsayt nokh di milkhome, tsvey khaveyrim vos zenen geven fun undzer shtot, ho'mir gemakht dos bild.

00:20:00.352 --> 00:20:01.370
in Munkhen.

00:20:01.123 --> 00:20:02.889
vi hobn zey geheysn, veyst ir?

